      "rationale": "Only a single ASTM F1717 static compression-bending configuration was tested. Dynamic and torsional loading conditions were not evaluated in this validation activity. This factor is below the required level; residual risk is accepted given the MEDIUM model influence and the conservative nature of the static test relative to fatigue failure modes addressed separately."
