      "rationale": "Three QoIs evaluated: construct stiffness (E/uval=1.43, 6.1% diff), yield force (E/uval=1.61, 8.2% diff), force at 40 mm (E/uval=1.78, 9.7% diff). All metrics within pre-established acceptance bounds. Validation metric computed per ASME V&V 40 Section 9."
