    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for a Medium model risk, Medium model influence, Medium decision consequence context of use. The single below-level factor (Test conditions, achieved=1 vs. required=2) is accepted given the conservative nature of the static compression-bending test and the corroborating multi-laboratory experimental dataset. Comprehensive Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification across all model inputs confirms that predicted QoIs remain within acceptance bounds across the full input distribution. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
    "decidedAt": "2026-04-19T00:00:00Z"
